</section>

<!-- 06 BRANDS -->
<section class="section section-gray">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">06 · Brands</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Commercial gas range brands we service.</h2>

    <ul class="brand-list">
      <li><strong>Vulcan</strong> (ITW Food Equipment Group). VR-24, VR-36, VR-48, VR-60, VR-72. Dominant LA install base. <a href="/brands/vulcan-range-repair/">Vulcan range repair brand page</a> and <a href="/brands/vulcan/">Vulcan brand hub</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>Garland</strong> (Welbilt). Master Series M. Common mid-tier install. <a href="/brands/garland-range-repair/">Garland range repair brand page</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>Wolf Commercial</strong> (Wolf Industrial / Sub-Zero Group). Challenger XL CHSC60. Premium tier. Distinct parts catalog from residential Wolf. <a href="/brands/wolf-range-repair/">Wolf range repair brand page</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>American Range</strong> (Cypress, CA, local manufacturer). Performer ARTGS series. LA-area pride. <a href="/brands/american-range-repair/">American Range repair brand page</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>Southbend</strong> (Middleby). Commercial gas ranges. <a href="/brands/southbend-oven-repair/">Southbend oven repair brand page</a> (range service available through same dispatch).</li>
      <li><strong>Imperial</strong> (Imperial Manufacturing). Imperial commercial cooking line. <a href="/brands/imperial-range-repair/">Imperial range repair brand page</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>Montague</strong> (Welbilt). Legend series. Premium tier. <a href="/brands/montague-oven-repair/">Montague oven repair brand page</a> (range service available through same dispatch).</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 07 WHY US -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">07 · Why operators call us</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Eight reasons.</h2>

    <ul class="why-list">
      <li><strong>Brand-specific failure pattern knowledge.</strong> Vulcan VR vs Garland M vs Wolf Challenger XL vs American Range Performer ARTGS. Each has different burner geometry and ignition tree.</li>
      <li><strong>LA gas pressure diagnostic.</strong> We test manifold pressure as a routine first step on multi-burner ignition issues. Pressure problems masquerade as multiple coincidental igniter failures.</li>
      <li><strong>Wolf Commercial vs residential disambiguation.</strong> Different parts catalogs, different authorized service networks. We verify by serial number and model prefix.</li>
      <li><strong>Common parts on the van.</strong> Vulcan VR igniters and thermocouples, Garland Master parts, common gas valves.</li>
      <li><strong>Annual and quarterly maintenance contracts.</strong> Predictable maintenance budget; high-volume operations benefit most.</li>
      <li><strong>BHGS #A49573 plus EPA 608 Universal certified (#1346255700410) scope.</strong> See our <a href="/credentials/licensed/">licensing page</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>$120 commercial diagnostic, no after-hours surcharge.</strong> Phones answered 24/7.</li>
      <li><strong>Same-day across LA, OC, Ventura.</strong> Next-day for Rancho Cucamonga and Temecula.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Sister sub-services: <a href="/commercial/range-repair/restaurant-range-salamander-repair/">restaurant range with salamander broiler</a>, <a href="/commercial/range-repair/french-top-range-repair/">French top range</a>. Sister pillars: <a href="/commercial/oven-repair/">commercial oven repair</a>, <a href="/commercial/grill-repair/">commercial grill repair</a>, <a href="/commercial/griddle-repair/">commercial griddle repair</a>, <a href="/commercial/charbroiler-repair/">commercial charbroiler repair</a>, <a href="/commercial/exhaust-hood-repair/">commercial exhaust hood repair</a> (Type I hood required for ranges). Parent: <a href="/commercial/range-repair/">commercial range repair pillar</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 08 FAQ -->
<section class="section section-gray">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">08 · FAQ</p>
